                              ReactiveML

                  http://www-spi.lip6.fr/~mandel/rml/


. Installation:
  ------------- 

To install ReactiveML in /usr/local:

  make install


To install ReactiveML in $PREFIX:

  make PREFIX=$PREFIX install

and you'll have to give to the compiler the path of the library by setting 
the RMLLIB environment variable to $PREFIX/lib/rml.
